snippet.title: Liar's Maze Trailer
snippet.description:
Just in time for this year's Halloween, celebrate the season with Alkaline and Zeggy in Space School's first ever spin-off game!
Download on Itch.io: https://darkchibishadow.itch.io/liarsmaze
Download on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=liars.maze

A short and sweet experience for all to enjoy, even those who haven't read the original comic. Game only takes about a hour or less to complete, download and enjoy to relax just for that time.
